

scripture Point 
    x of atom
    y of atom 


salm bresenham receiving s of Point and f of Point reveals legion of Point
    let there raw_dx be x from f minus x from s
    let there raw_dy be y from f minus y from s

    let there be xIncr
    let there be yIncr

    let there points be hail legion of Point praying s

    whether raw_dx lesser than 0
       xIncr become -1
    otherwise 
        xIncr become 1 

    whether raw_dy lesser than 0
        yIncr become -1
    otherwise 
        yIncr become 1

    let there dx be hail abs praying raw_dx
    let there dy be hail abs praying raw_dy
        
    let there counter be 0
    let there x be x from s
    let there y be y from s

    whether dx no lesser than dy
        let there p be 2 times dy minus dx

        litany for counter lesser than dx
            x become x plus xIncr

            whether p no lesser than 0
                y become y plus yIncr
                p become p plus 2 times after dy minus dx
            otherwise 
                p become p plus 2 times dy

            points become hail push upon points praying manifest Point praying x and y
            counter become counter plus 1
    otherwise
        let there p be 2 times dx minus dy

        litany for counter lesser than dy
            x become x plus xIncr

            whether p greater than 0
                y become y plus yIncr
                p become p plus 2 times after dy minus dx
            otherwise 
                p become p plus 2 times dy
            
            points become hail push upon points praying manifest Point praying x and y

            counter become counter plus 1
    reveal points



hail proclaim praying hail bresenham praying manifest Point praying -1 and 4 thus and manifest Point praying 5 and 7
 
amen